general.desc: PT Distribusi Voucher Nusantara Tbk provides business-to-business and business-to-customer software solutions. The company's operating segment includes Digital products and services; Tours and travel and Digital financial services, Micro-logistics Services, and Advertising. It generates maximum revenue from the Digital products and services segment. The company's products include Diva Intelligent IM and Diva Chat Commerce.
